is_randomForest.Rd

Check whether or not the model is a certain model. Checks if a model is made with: randomForest::randomForest, ranger::ranger, gbm::gbm, xgboost::xgb.train, catboost::catboost.train, or lightgbm::lightgbm.

is_randomForest(model)

is_ranger(model)

is_gbm(model)

is_xgboost(model)

is_lightgbm(model)

is_catboost(model)

Arguments

model

A model object to check the class/origin.

Value

A logical, whether or not the model is of a certain class.

library(cheem)

dat  <- amesHousing2018_NorthAmes

# treeshap handles various tree-based models:

  lgbm_params <- list(objective = "regression", num_leaves = 25)
